data.title: Preity Zinta applauds Salman Khan and Shah Rukh Khan; Punjab Kings co-owner admires Virat Kohli's 'on field aggression'
meta_keywords: Preity Zinta shah rukh khanm Preity Zinta salman khan
Preity Zinta shares heartfelt praise for Virat Kohli
data.meta_description: Bollywood beauty Preity Zinta is known for her active engagement with fans across various social media platforms. Recently, she participated in an Ask Me Anything session on her X handle, where a curious fan sought her insights into her colleagues, Shah Rukh Khan, Salman Khan, and cricketer Virat Kohli. Preity responded by showering praise upon both her former co-stars, highlighting Shah Rukh Khan's entertaining and competitive nature, offering fans a glimpse into the camaraderie shared behind the scenes. Another fan inquired about a potential collaboration with a co-star from the movie 'Dunki' for a new project, to which Preity responded with enthusiasm for a mind-blowing script. When asked about her views on her 'Har Dil Jo Pyaar Karega' co-star Salman Khan, Preity praised his exceptional qualities, describing him as a loyal friend and an incredibly talented actor with a heart of gold. Additionally, Preity expressed admiration for cricketer Virat Kohli, emphasizing his love for family and his dance moves. Preity's forthcoming project, 'Lahore 1947,' featuring Sunny Deol and Karan Deol, has garnered anticipation among fans eagerly awaiting her next on-screen appearance.
